column5: Hope you have a super day! I guess you're aware that it was on this day in 1586 Johan van Oldenbarnevelt became the Dutch chief legal advisor? Tonight when you're sitting around the dinner table, you might want to impress the kids with that tidbit.
All the best to ya young feller !!
Happy bday "Spawn of Ed" for sure.. lol
Happy Birthday Marty best of the day to you bud.   Art
Best wishes to you today and always my young friend.
Happy Birthday ya ole bugger  Hope you have a great day!
I was going to say Happy Birthday "Spawn of Ed" but someone beat me to it ...  So I'll just say Happy Birthday Marty, I hope it was a great day spent with friends and family
